        <para>The system is integrated into the cab to provide a built-in appearance. The heater, evaporator core,
            blower and other parts of the system are located in the Blend-Air unit under the passenger seat. Heating and
            cooling controls along with a blower motor control are located in the cab and sleeper compartment.
        </para>
        <para>For greater detail in servicing the air conditioning system, refer to the following manuals, as necessary,
            for the model being serviced. (Manuals are located in the Master Service Manual.)
